4 STEP ROUTINE: ⁣
1 - Detangle hair w/ wide tooth comb ⁣
2 - wet hair and apply shampoo ( Down Under Naturals Shampoo - Rasberry Splash ) ⁣
 3 - Apply conditioner ( @allnaturalkinks ) ⁣
 4 - detangle using brush from Dollar Tree ⁣
 5 - Go for a swim 🐳⁣
⁣
disclaimer: no fishies 🐠🐟 were harmed by the products I used on my hair 💙⁣
